overview: " Nakajima Miyuki Concert" Ichikai "2015-2016 " (Nakajima Miyuki Concert Ichie Nisenjugo ni Senjurokuro) is a live video and live album of Miyuki Nakajima released on November 16, 2016 ( --LIVE SELECTION-).  It is recorded from the concert tour "Ichikai 2015-2016" held from November 12, 2015 to February 11, 2016 .
title: Nakajima Miyuki Concert "Ichie" 2015~2016 -LIVE SELECTION
